        <h3>How It Works – Simple Steps</h3>
        <ol class="card" style="padding:16px 22px">
          <li><strong>Intake & Reports.</strong> Fill out the intake form and upload your ID and proof of address. We securely review your credit reports or meet face‑to‑face, one‑on‑one.</li>
          <li><strong>Consultation ($150).</strong> We go through your reports together, identify what's wrong, and choose the timeline category A, B, or C.</li>
          <li><strong>Monthly Work ($99/mo).</strong> Targeted disputes, tracking responses, and updates. First 10 inquiries are free; each extra is $15.</li>
          <li><strong>Monitor & Adjust.</strong> We follow up with bureaus and furnishers, send additional rounds if needed, and keep you posted.</li>
          <li><strong>Results & Next Steps.</strong> When items are resolved or verified, we plan positive next steps to keep you moving forward.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>What We Work On</h3>
        <ul class="checklist">
          <li>Wrong personal info (misspelled names, wrong SSN digits, wrong DOB, addresses)</li>
          <li>Wrong or missing account digits, duplicate accounts, mixed files</li>
          <li>Inquiries: review + removal requests</li>
          <li>Late payments, identity theft items</li>
          <li>Serious items like repossession and bankruptcy</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
